Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,早間新聞由巴頓電視台為您播報
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\bord1\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(662.4,584.333)}國王陛下99歲生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,今天國王陛下在道瓦的城堡迎來99歲生日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,已經這麼大歲數了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:23.12,Comment,,0,0,0,,今天各地會舉辦典禮為國王慶生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是這個國家的和平象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.13,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你太悠閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.71,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  蘿塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天開始出差
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不早說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有東西要準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我等著你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,煙盒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,專屬物件忘了怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,蹭煙的吉恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,吉恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要來一根嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.67,0:01:28.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Watch your back, attack is on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,So feel around with the cards you play
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.20,0:01:32.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Lookin' out, suspicion, for they keep deceivin'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Aim for every minute that you believe is right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HDDE2F4&\3c&H000000&\bord1\blur2}Silhouette conspiracies indefinite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HDDE2F4&\3c&H000000&\bord1\blur2}Never fool, gotta stay cool. Smoke another cigarette
