Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,見つけたIllusion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.61,0:02:07.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,儚いストーリー繋がるSeasonへ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on! ねぇ、come on! On a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:11.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,探してる鍵を (Where's the key?)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:14.80,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Just move and you'll find out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:15.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:17.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on! On a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:19.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,ねぇ 知りたいでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:23.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,描く場所に辿り着くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:25.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,Come on! ねぇ、come on! On a journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:31.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,運命が呼び寄せた導きの証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F7F0&\3c&HF1F7F0&\bord0.5}Stay cool! It's never really what it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:38.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF1F7F0&\3c&HF1F7F0&\bord0.5}You gotta use your eyes to perceive the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:44.84,Comment,,0,0,0,,是煙
